{"tid":1301523,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[推!] 金鐘海富連儂牆！將絕食者精神發揚光大","createTime":"2019-07-09T16:10:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T17:21:37.000Z","uid":146673,"like":55,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"50dac39cb3d680f0c53d6f96124b640a0e71e0d1","tid":1301523,"uid":146673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:10:52.000Z","msg":"啱啱去咗探伯伯，<br />\n伯伯除咗聲沙之外，都尚算精神，<br />\n現場都一直有人睇住佢，有足夠物資<br />\n<br />\n但真係諗諗計喺聽日記者會前<br />\n將金鐘連儂牆發揚光大，<br />\n因為伯伯真係好重視聽日嘅記者會，<br />\n唔肯休息，諗梗記者會嘅對策。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然伯伯一直叫我哋唔好擔心同操心<br />\n但至少我哋要幫手令到聽日記者會搞得好好睇睇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係剩係對住自己嗰區嘅連儂牆打飛機！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地一把年紀都仲咁樣為我地抗爭，我地唔可以辜負佢㗎！<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊諗諗計仲有乜嘢係可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z69UaMw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ69UaMw.png&h=4d87f156&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"419154655329bf64331d3bdc90a1497e82236ee2","tid":1301523,"uid":146673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:11:04.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"5ec45151efb51bc09296bcbd1a05e571d5e6f3bf","tid":1301523,"uid":146673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:11:15.000Z","msg":"自推！"},{"pid":"726478aa08eaf1ad6add371a70180b7a18f5efb8","tid":1301523,"uid":69753,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:11:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>7.10</strong> - <ins>麥小姐追思會</ins> ＠ 中環愛丁堡廣場 - 19:00~22:30<br />\n<strong>7.11</strong> - <ins>梁烈士公眾告別禮</ins> - <a href=\"http://t.me/leung711\" data-sr-ur